title: Two Whats?! And A Wow! - The Stars of Space
description:
Why are Mindy and Guy Raz filling out job applications? And what does that have to do with astronauts?! We've got the questions AND the answers on today's galactic round of Two Whats?! And A Wow! We're challenging you to separate the facts from the fiction about animal astronauts!
